<h2 class="sectionedit5" id="लघु">लघु</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
32 आदैच्च वृद्धिसंज्ञः स्यात् ॥
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT5 SECTION "लघु" [1105-1210] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit6" id="सिद्धान्तकौमुदी">सिद्धान्तकौमुदी</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
<a href="http://avg-sanskrit.org/sutras/1-1-70.html" class="wikilink1" title="sutras:1-1-70">&lt;&lt; 1-1-70</a> – <a href="http://avg-sanskrit.org/sutras/1-1-2.html" class="wikilink1" title="sutras:1-1-2">1-1-2 &gt;&gt;</a><br/>

